{"tid":2398418,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"東莞扶貧騷 窮困戶住別墅  旋轉樓梯配大理石牆 網民：發過美國","createTime":"2021-02-07T09:29:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-07T11:07:34.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"9d19ff038005eee23f9f888fe679e2460fcc2010","tid":2398418,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T09:29:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210207/45X46L7M4ZG4DCCW2D267UVB3E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210207%2F45X46L7M4ZG4DCCW2D267UVB3E%2F&d=NdDBecmRZzhky7sLgKmJOdiuVIf%2Fu6affRELz7PmdGA%3D&h=7a378728\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210207%2F45X46L7M4ZG4DCCW2D267UVB3E%2F&h=b4eee907\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210207/45X46L7M4ZG4DCCW2D267UVB3E/</a><br />\n<br />\n東莞扶貧騷 窮困戶住別墅 <br />\n旋轉樓梯配大理石牆 網民：發過美國<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/f3V9VFxAkgCD5MhcBLYzcCKmRt8=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/T7Q3MTYJCJGKDM4SWHDMS4FOU4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Ff3V9VFxAkgCD5MhcBLYzcCKmRt8%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FT7Q3MTYJCJGKDM4SWHDMS4FOU4.jpg&h=5da6bd67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■東莞官員探望困難戶，但受訪者居所寬敞兼裝修豪華，惹人懷疑。<br />\n<br />\n繼山東青島官員探訪「茅台貧困戶」後，東莞長安鎮幹部又被指慰問「別墅貧困戶」，所謂的困難家庭竟住豪華別墅，家中更有旋轉樓梯。網民直斥造假，揶揄按照此等貧困戶水平，東莞市怕是比美國更發達。居民委員會解釋，幹部探訪的對象是一名受傷老人家，屬於春節慰問對象，並非貧困人口，而他受傷後暫住女兒家養傷。<br />\n<br />\n東莞長安鎮上角社區居委會上周五（5日）在公眾號，發表《鎮黨委委員戴浩平走訪慰問社區困難家庭》一文。不過配圖照片卻出現疑似旋轉樓梯、名貴皮梳化和大理石牆面，裝潢豪華，被網民質疑是形式主義、「富人區裏的最窮一戶」。輿論在網上發酵一整天，居委會隨後解釋，慰問對象為一名71歲盧姓男子，去年中因交通意外受傷，當局遂把他納入春節的慰問名單。<br />\n<br />\n居委會又指，盧老在受。。。<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n資料顯示，長安鎮是東莞第一強鎮，在全國千強鎮中排名第七，全鎮有五家上市企業，2019年GDP突破700億元人民幣（下同，839億港元）。當地因扶貧成為焦點已非首次，早在2019年5月，長安鎮湧頭村有家庭月入16,000元（19,182港元）都被評為困難戶，當時官方解釋指，該家庭中有人身患重病、要花近百萬醫療費。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/IQ1rYk5J-LMlHA7qF2EJD6sxlgs=/646x552/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6OS6JHFILFGNDMGXBQW7FHVBM4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FIQ1rYk5J-LMlHA7qF2EJD6sxlgs%3D%2F646x552%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6OS6JHFILFGNDMGXBQW7FHVBM4.jpg&h=be4927e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■青島官員也慰問貧困戶，受訪者家中卻出現茅台、五糧液（紅圈示）等名酒。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n青島窮戶有茅台五糧液<br />\n<br />\n南有東莞「別墅貧困戶」，北有青島「茅台貧困戶」。青島棘洪灘街道辦事處近日發佈一篇文章，講述領導走訪困難家庭，不過照片中的單位裝修亮麗，還有兩瓶茅台、一瓶五糧液，還有疑似名牌電視機和跑步機手桿，同惹爭議。街。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n兩宗官員探訪貧困戶原。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n據公開資料，國家對貧困戶的界定有嚴格劃分，絕對貧困是年人均收入低於752港元，低收入為年人均收入1,038港元至1,444港元。慰問困難戶為政府部門、組織在特定時期的政治任務，而且探訪對象一般是在本地人範圍內找。<br />\n<br />\n微信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/iitl2L0f_xJT9GO2714QbNHcmUs=/471x697/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/B7VD4FJEDNEIJMJFCP5GLMYSWE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fiitl2L0f_xJT9GO2714QbNHcmUs%3D%2F471x697%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FB7VD4FJEDNEIJMJFCP5GLMYSWE.jpg&h=0c36022f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9745b12e9257f168d615ec1f2bd6910c761a0cd4","tid":2398418,"uid":3776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T09:39:26.000Z","msg":"進入小康<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"141cbc6f93bfbbc658c5d9a8900af7454c619402","tid":2398418,"uid":42548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T09:41:14.000Z","msg":"呢個世界真係公平公正<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wa